11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:415:\"<p>Looking for an easy way to fix broken links in WordPress? It can be time-consuming to find and fix broken links across an entire website. But in this article, you&#8217;ll learn an easy way to discover and fix broken links.&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/fix-broken-links-in-wordpress/\">How to Find and Fix Broken Links in WordPress</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Sherrie Gossett\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27328:\"<p>Looking for an easy way to fix broken links in WordPress?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It can be time-consuming to find and fix broken links across an entire website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But in this article, you&#8217;ll learn an easy way to discover and fix broken links.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What you’ll need</strong>: <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/blc-pricing-upgrade/\">Broken Link Checker by AIOSEO</a></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-whats-a-broken-link\">What’s a Broken Link?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-why-fix-broken-links\">Why Fix Broken Links?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-fix-broken-links-in-wordpress\">How to Fix Broken Links in WordPress</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-1-download-and-install-the-broken-link-checker-plugin\">Step 1: Download and Install the Broken Link Checker Plugin</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-2-review-broken-links\">Step 2: Review Broken Links</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-3-fix-broken-links\">Step 3: Fix Broken Links</a><ul></ul></li></ul></div>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-whats-a-broken-link\">What’s a Broken Link?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A broken link is a URL that doesn’t work. A URL is the <strong>address</strong>, expressed as a hyperlink, of an online file.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>These hyperlinks (or “links” for short) connect us to things on the web.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And each page or file has a unique address (URL).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, this is the URL for the AIOSEO homepage.</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>https:&#47;&#47;aioseo.com</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>And this is the URL for the AIOSEO blog.</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>https:&#47;&#47;aioseo.com/blog</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>Hyperlinks (URLs) may point to:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>A web page like a blog post or YouTube video.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>A file, like an image, PDF, or audio recording.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-theme-notice-box\" role=\"alert\">\n<p>URL stands for Uniform Resource Locator.</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p>When a link is broken, it doesn’t take us where it’s supposed to. Instead, we get an error message like this one.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"947\" height=\"317\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/404-page-not-found-message.png\" alt=\"404 page not found message\" class=\"wp-image-187745\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/404-page-not-found-message.png 947w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/404-page-not-found-message-300x100.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/404-page-not-found-message-768x257.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/404-page-not-found-message-600x201.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/404-page-not-found-message-179x60.png 179w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/404-page-not-found-message-269x90.png 269w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So a broken link is like a <strong>wrong address</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Imagine you drive to the hardware store but didn&#8217;t know they moved. You show up, and there&#8217;s just a vacant building there.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Similarly, when your site visitors click on a broken link, they don&#8217;t find what they were looking for.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-why-fix-broken-links\">Why Fix Broken Links?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s a good idea to fix broken links because if site visitors can’t find what they’re looking for, they might leave without converting.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also lose sales if links to your product or subscription pages are broken.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The problem is no one has time to search every web page on a site and check every link. Plus, when we have a broken link, it’s often by accident. So we’re usually unaware that there’s even a problem.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, what&#8217;s the easy way to find and fix these issues?</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-to-fix-broken-links-in-wordpress\">How to Fix Broken Links in WordPress</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You can use a plugin that automatically finds all broken links on your site and provides button-click fixes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For this tutorial, we&#8217;ll be using the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing-broken-link-checker/\" title=\"\"><strong>Broken Link Checker</strong> plugin</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you can click a button, you’re good to go. The plugin does the hard work.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This plugin is from the All in One SEO (AIOSEO) team, makers of the SEO plugin of the same name.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All in One SEO is an established software company with thousands of 5-star reviews on WordPress.org and over 3 million users.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-step-1-download-and-install-the-broken-link-checker-plugin\">Step 1: Download and Install the Broken Link Checker Plugin</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The first step is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing-broken-link-checker/\" title=\"\">downloading</a> and installing the Broken Link Checker plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-link-checker-aioseo-1024x315.png\" alt=\"homepage of broken link checker plugin\" class=\"wp-image-187746\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-link-checker-aioseo-1024x315.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-link-checker-aioseo-300x92.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-link-checker-aioseo-768x237.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-link-checker-aioseo-600x185.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-link-checker-aioseo-292x90.png 292w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-link-checker-aioseo.png 1123w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-how-to-install-broken-link-checker\">How to Install Broken Link Checker</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you&#8217;ve downloaded the zip file, in WordPress, go to <strong>Plugins » Add New</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"339\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/wordpress-add-new-plugin-1024x339.png\" alt=\"screengrab of wordpress dashboard plugins button\" class=\"wp-image-187747\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/wordpress-add-new-plugin-1024x339.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/wordpress-add-new-plugin-300x99.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/wordpress-add-new-plugin-768x255.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/wordpress-add-new-plugin-1536x509.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/wordpress-add-new-plugin-2048x679.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/wordpress-add-new-plugin-600x199.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/wordpress-add-new-plugin-181x60.png 181w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/wordpress-add-new-plugin-272x90.png 272w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Then click <strong>Upload Plugins</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"221\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/upload-wordpress-plugin-1024x221.png\" alt=\"screengrab of wordpress upload plugin button\" class=\"wp-image-187749\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/upload-wordpress-plugin-1024x221.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/upload-wordpress-plugin-300x65.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/upload-wordpress-plugin-768x166.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/upload-wordpress-plugin-600x129.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/upload-wordpress-plugin-190x41.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/upload-wordpress-plugin-417x90.png 417w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/upload-wordpress-plugin.png 1441w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Select the zip file from your desktop and upload it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A setup wizard will walk you through a few steps.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ll be asked to create an account.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"830\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/blc-trial-checkout-1024x830.jpg\" alt=\"broken link checker checkout page\" class=\"wp-image-187750\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/blc-trial-checkout-1024x830.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/blc-trial-checkout-300x243.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/blc-trial-checkout-768x622.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/blc-trial-checkout-1536x1244.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/blc-trial-checkout-2048x1659.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/blc-trial-checkout-600x486.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/blc-trial-checkout-74x60.jpg 74w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/blc-trial-checkout-111x90.jpg 111w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Then you&#8217;ll be asked to connect to your license.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/connect-blc-1024x961.jpg\" alt=\"broken link checker choose a license window\" class=\"wp-image-187751\" width=\"512\" height=\"481\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/connect-blc-1024x961.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/connect-blc-300x282.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/connect-blc-768x721.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/connect-blc-1536x1442.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/connect-blc-600x563.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/connect-blc-64x60.jpg 64w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/connect-blc-96x90.jpg 96w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/connect-blc.jpg 1729w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you&#8217;ve clicked <strong>Connect,</strong> you&#8217;ll see a message: &#8220;<strong>Your account is connected!</strong>&#8220;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Beneath that, you’ll see<strong> a Link Tweaks </strong>section with 2 toggle buttons. We recommend you toggle both these buttons <em>on</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Then click the big <strong>Save Changes</strong> button at the bottom right.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"593\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/link-tweaks-1024x593.png\" alt=\"link tweaks settings for broken link checker plugin\" class=\"wp-image-187752\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/link-tweaks-1024x593.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/link-tweaks-300x174.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/link-tweaks-768x445.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/link-tweaks-1536x889.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/link-tweaks-2048x1186.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/link-tweaks-600x347.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/link-tweaks-104x60.png 104w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/link-tweaks-155x90.png 155w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-step-2-review-broken-links\">Step 2: Review Broken Links</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, to see and review your broken links, click on the <strong>Broken Links</strong> tab.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"774\" height=\"414\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-links-tab.png\" alt=\"broken links button in broken link checker plugin\" class=\"wp-image-187753\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-links-tab.png 774w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-links-tab-300x160.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-links-tab-768x411.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-links-tab-600x321.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-links-tab-112x60.png 112w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-links-tab-168x90.png 168w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You’ll see all your internal and external links categorized by link status:</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">All (all links) | <strong>Broken | </strong>Redirects | Dismissed</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Click on the <strong>Broken</strong> tab to see your list of broken links.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"489\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-links-examples-1024x489.png\" alt=\"list of broken links in broken link checker plugin\" class=\"wp-image-187755\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-links-examples-1024x489.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-links-examples-300x143.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-links-examples-768x367.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-links-examples-1536x734.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-links-examples-2048x978.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-links-examples-600x287.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-links-examples-126x60.png 126w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-links-examples-188x90.png 188w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In the example above, we have 3 broken links, listed in the left-hand column.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-step-3-fix-broken-links\">Step 3: Fix Broken Links</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Hover your cursor over a broken link and 4 options will display beneath it: Choose <strong>Edit URL</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"523\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-1024x523.png\" alt=\"fix broken links with edit url feature\" class=\"wp-image-174472\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-1024x523.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-300x153.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-768x392.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-1536x784.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-2048x1046.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-600x306.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-118x60.png 118w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/fix-broken-link-176x90.png 176w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You’ll now see a field displaying the <em>anchor text</em> (at left) and the <em>broken URL</em> (at right).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Simply type the correct URL into that field and click the blue <strong>Update</strong> button at the lower left.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In our example above, the Wikipedia page we linked to no longer exists. In cases like this, you’ll need to search to find the new page URL or simply replace it with an alternate URL.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another option is to click <strong>Unlink</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-the-unlink-option\">The Unlink Option</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Clicking <strong>Unlink</strong> will remove the link from the post.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"631\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/unlink-1024x631.png\" alt=\"unlink option in broken link checker plugin\" class=\"wp-image-187756\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/unlink-1024x631.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/unlink-300x185.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/unlink-768x474.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/unlink-1536x947.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/unlink-600x370.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/unlink-97x60.png 97w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/unlink-146x90.png 146w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/unlink.png 1669w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-step-4-optional-recheck-links\">Step 4: (Optional) Recheck Links</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you’ve fixed the link, click <strong>Recheck</strong> to test it and confirm it’s been fixed.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"631\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-link-checker-recheck-1024x631.png\" alt=\"recheck option in broken link checker plugin\" class=\"wp-image-187757\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-link-checker-recheck-1024x631.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-link-checker-recheck-300x185.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-link-checker-recheck-768x474.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-link-checker-recheck-1536x947.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-link-checker-recheck-600x370.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-link-checker-recheck-97x60.png 97w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-link-checker-recheck-146x90.png 146w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/broken-link-checker-recheck.png 1669w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Note: When Broken Link Checker rechecks a link, automatically checks all links on that page. Those link checks will be deducted from your monthly allotment of link checks. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-to-use-broken-link-checkers-advanced-settings\">How to Use Broken Link Checker’s Advanced Settings</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Broken Link Checker will scan your site every 3 days. You can choose which types of pages are scanned by tweaking the <strong>Advanced Settings</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Go to <strong>Broken Link Checker</strong> <strong>» Settings.</strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Scroll down and click the toggle button next to <strong>Advanced Settings</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"597\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/advanced-settings-1024x597.png\" alt=\"advanced settings in broken link checker plugin\" class=\"wp-image-187758\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/advanced-settings-1024x597.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/advanced-settings-300x175.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/advanced-settings-768x448.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/advanced-settings-1536x895.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/advanced-settings-2048x1194.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/advanced-settings-600x350.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/advanced-settings-103x60.png 103w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/advanced-settings-154x90.png 154w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The default setting is <strong>Include All Post Types</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Untick the boxes next to any post type you want to omit from scanning. The options are:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Published</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Draft</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Private</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Scheduled (future)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Pending.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-seo-settings\">SEO Settings</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you go back to your WordPress dashboard, and mouseover the Broken Link Checker icon, you’ll see an SEO Settings option.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That will take you to a splash page with information about the All in One SEO (AIOSEO) Plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We recommend that you <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">download All in One SEO</a> as well. This plugin makes many technical SEO tasks as simple as clicking some buttons and filling out forms.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are a few features of the plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"520\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-site-score-1024x520.png\" alt=\"aioseo site score example\" class=\"wp-image-187759\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-site-score-1024x520.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-site-score-300x152.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-site-score-768x390.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-site-score-1536x780.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-site-score-2048x1040.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-site-score-600x305.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-site-score-118x60.png 118w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-site-score-177x90.png 177w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>SEO score: </strong>Get an instant <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-perform-website-seo-analysis-on-wordpress/\">SEO Analysis</a> with recommendations for improving your homepage.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>On-Page SEO</strong>: For each web page, you’ll see simple recommendations for improving SEO.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Breadcrumbs</strong>: Click a button to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/displaying-breadcrumbs-on-your-site/\">add breadcrumb navigation</a> to your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Local SEO</strong>: Small business owners can set up their <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/local-business-seo-for-a-single-location/\">local SEO basics</a> with a few clicks.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-rich-snippets-to-wordpress/\"><strong>Rich snippets</strong></a>: Make your pages eligible for super-deluxe search engine displays with our click-button tool. (Store owners can add <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-product-review-schema-in-wordpress/\">product review schema</a>.)</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Sitemaps</strong>: By default, AIOSEO automatically creates an <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/how-to-create-an-xml-sitemap/\">XML sitemap</a> and an <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/how-to-create-an-rss-sitemap/\">RSS sitemap</a> for you. These sitemaps help search engines understand and index your site.\n<ul>\n<li>And you can easily turn on (with a button click) an <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/html-sitemap/\">HTML sitemap</a>, which can help your readers discover new content.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Pro version users can turn on a <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/how-to-create-a-video-sitemap/\">Video sitemap</a> or <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/how-to-create-a-google-news-sitemap/\">Google News sitemap</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"643\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-seo-analysis-1024x643.png\" alt=\"aioseo complete seo checklist feature\" class=\"wp-image-187760\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-seo-analysis-1024x643.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-seo-analysis-300x188.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-seo-analysis-768x482.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-seo-analysis-1536x964.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-seo-analysis-2048x1286.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-seo-analysis-600x377.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-seo-analysis-96x60.png 96w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-complete-seo-checklist-seo-analysis-143x90.png 143w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you know how to find and fix broken links, you may have some additional questions.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-are-broken-links-bad-for-seo\">Are Broken Links Bad for SEO?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Broken links may or may not be bad for SEO, depending on the context.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As mentioned, broken links typically lead to 404 error pages. There&#8217;s nothing inherently wrong with 404 pages: this error code tells search engines that the requested page no longer exists.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In fact, Google has said that 404 error messages are a <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/search/blog/2011/05/do-404s-hurt-my-site\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">normal part of the web</a> and don&#8217;t impact ranking.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-botched-website-migrations\">Botched Website Migrations</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>However, if your site has lots of broken links, that could affect your ranking. This scenario sometimes happens when a website is moved to a new platform (like from Drupal to Joomla), and the site structure (folder structure) is radically changed.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this scenario, almost all the URLs change. The problem comes when the original URLs are not <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/redirection-manager/\"><strong>redirected</strong></a> to the new ones.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All those old broken URLs will still be indexed and present in search results. But because those pages are now inaccessible, Google will quickly remove them from search results.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That can lead to the loss of most of your website traffic.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"All in One SEO&#039;s Redirect Manager Feature\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IdY9CzaD2Vk?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>See how AIOSEO&#8217;s Redirection Manager works. </em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Website migration is a tricky subject. Consider consulting with an SEO professional before moving to a new platform or making any big changes to your site structure.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-whats-next\">What’s Next?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you find and fix broken links in WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, see why <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/referring-domains-vs-backlinks-seo/\" title=\"\">backlinks impact SEO</a>. And learn how to <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/lead-generation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">turn traffic into leads</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/fix-broken-links-in-wordpress/\">How to Find and Fix Broken Links in WordPress</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"https://aioseo.com/fix-broken-links-in-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\