\"data\";s:8:\"SEO Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Beginner SEO\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"DIY SEO\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"WordPress SEO for beginners\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=185235\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:439:\"<p>Would you like to learn DIY SEO? Whether you&#8217;re a blogger or a small business owner, taking a do-it-yourself approach to SEO can be rewarding. Since SEO is foundational to modern business, you&#8217;ll quickly learn what action steps are required&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/diy-seo-projects-for-beginners/\">DIY SEO: 4 Easy Projects to Get Started</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Sherrie Gossett\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39603:\"<p>Would you like to learn DIY SEO? Whether you&#8217;re a blogger or a small business owner, taking a do-it-yourself approach to SEO can be rewarding.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Since SEO is foundational to modern business, you&#8217;ll quickly learn what action steps are required for online success.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>DIY SEO will not only help you achieve your site goals, it can also lay a foundation for a new career.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-seo\">What is SEO?</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-download-all-in-one-seo-aioseo-plugin\">Download All in One SEO (AIOSEO) Plugin</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-project-1-sitemaps\">Project 1: Sitemaps</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-project-2-local-seo-for-small-businesses\">Project 2: Local SEO (for Small Businesses)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-project-3-optimize-content-for-seo\">Project 3: Optimize Content for SEO</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-project-4-optimize-titles-and-meta-descriptions\">Project 4: Optimize Titles and Meta Descriptions</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-more-diy-seo-projects\">More DIY SEO Projects</a><ul></ul></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-what-is-seo\">What is SEO?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>SEO, or search engine optimization, is the practice of optimizing web pages so that they rank well in search engine results pages (SERPs).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We&#8217;ve all heard someone say, &#8220;I want to rank well in Google.&#8221; Here, we need to ask: &#8220;<strong><em>Which</em></strong> web pages do you want to rank well and <strong><em>for what keyword</em></strong>?&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is because search engine results appear <em>after</em> you type (or speak) a request into Google. (This request is called a <strong>search query</strong> or a <strong>keyword</strong>.)</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-theme-notice-box\" role=\"alert\">\n<p>Even though &#8220;keyword&#8221; is singular it also refers to phrases</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, if we search for &#8220;<strong>growth consultant</strong>&#8221; this website below has the #1 ranking for that keyword.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/featured-snippet-example-1024x512.jpg\" alt=\"featured snippet example\" class=\"wp-image-185497\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/featured-snippet-example-1024x512.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/featured-snippet-example-300x150.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/featured-snippet-example-768x384.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/featured-snippet-example-1536x768.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/featured-snippet-example-2048x1024.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/featured-snippet-example-600x300.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/featured-snippet-example-120x60.jpg 120w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/featured-snippet-example-180x90.jpg 180w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So we can say that the above article ranks in the #1 spot for &#8220;growth consultant.&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For a web page to &#8220;rank well&#8221; it needs to be targeting a <strong>specific keyword</strong>. (You&#8217;ll learn more about targeting keywords, later in this article.)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As you move forward with DIY SEO, you&#8217;ll:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Identify your most important web pages. (These may be product pages.)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Optimize your site and individual pages.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Create new content based on keywords you want to rank well for.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-types-of-seo\">Types of SEO</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Before we get to the fun part, let&#8217;s take a brief look at different types of SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-on-page-seo-vs-off-page-seo\">On-Page SEO vs. Off-Page SEO</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>On-Page SEO refers to optimization actions you take on your website. And &#8220;off-page SEO&#8221; (or &#8220;off-site SEO&#8221;) refers to marketing actions like social media posting or writing guest posts for respected websites. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can think of off-page SEO as <strong>online reputation management</strong>: when other sites and people &#8220;vouch&#8221; for your website that can boost your SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-technical-seo\">Technical SEO</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Technical SEO usually refers to intermediate or advanced-level tactics like generating sitemaps or adding schema markup to your pages. (We&#8217;ll address these shortly.)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress site owners can use an SEO plugin, like<a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\"> All in One SEO (AIOSEO)</a>, to handle these tasks automatically or with a few button clicks.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-benefits-of-seo\">Benefits of SEO</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>SEO is one of the few marketing strategies that can be used to reach a target audience at any stage.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Awareness</strong>: This is when they first learn about your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Consideration</strong>: At this stage they&#8217;re exploring what you offer.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Action</strong>: Then they convert and buy from you.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Remember: the traffic acquired by SEO is <strong>free traffic</strong>. It&#8217;s not paid advertising. In marketing, this free traffic is called <em>organic traffic</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Even better, you can learn to select keywords (topics) to write about that are likely to lead to <em><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/exit-intent-popup-examples/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">conversions</a></em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For example: of these keywords below, which one indicates the searcher is <em>ready to buy</em>?</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>types of decks</li>\n\n\n\n<li>outdoor deck ideas</li>\n\n\n\n<li>hire a deck builder</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>If you picked the 3rd one, move to the head of the class.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As your optimized content rises in search rankings, it will <em>increase</em> your conversions and sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-download-all-in-one-seo-aioseo-plugin\">Download All in One SEO (AIOSEO) Plugin</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To get started with your first WordPress DIY SEO projects, we recommend you download and install the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">All in One SEO (AIOSEO) plugin</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This SEO plugin is designed to be easy for beginners to use yet it&#8217;s effective in producing professional results.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"606\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-homepage-1024x606.jpg\" alt=\"aioseo homepage\" class=\"wp-image-185257\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-homepage-1024x606.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-homepage-300x178.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-homepage-768x455.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-homepage-1536x910.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-homepage-2048x1213.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-homepage-600x355.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-homepage-101x60.jpg 101w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-homepage-152x90.jpg 152w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We recommend the Pro version of the plugin because it includes a <strong>Link Assistant</strong> that makes internal link-building easy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Follow the instructions below to download and install the AIOSEO plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Download <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">the AIOSEO plugin</a>. (It downloads as a zip file. Don&#8217;t open the zip file.)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>In your WordPress editor, go to <strong>Plugins » Add New</strong>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Upload</strong> the zip file.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>A setup wizard will walk you through some simple steps.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Questions? Follow <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\">this guide</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-project-1-sitemaps\">Project 1: Sitemaps</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sitemaps are maps of your web content designed primarily for search engines to read. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here&#8217;s an example of a sitemap: <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/sitemap.xml\">https://aioseo.com/sitemap.xml</a></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"535\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-1024x535.png\" alt=\"xml sitemap example\" class=\"wp-image-185484\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-1024x535.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-300x157.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-768x401.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-600x313.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-115x60.png 115w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-172x90.png 172w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap.png 1323w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>This is a screengrab of the XML sitemap for aioseo.com. As you scroll down the page, the other site URLs are shown.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Your website should have a sitemap and it needs to be updated each time you publish or edit an article.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-xml-and-rss-sitemaps-automatically-generated\">XML and RSS Sitemaps: Automatically Generated</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Here&#8217;s where the All in One SEO (AIOSEO) plugin saves you time. It automatically generates an <strong>XML and an RSS sitemap</strong> for you. And these sitemaps will update themselves. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Wondering how these 2 kinds of sitemaps differ? </p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>XML sitemaps contain all URLs on a website. </li>\n\n\n\n<li>RSS sitemaps notify search engines of <em>recent updates</em>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>There is one thing you&#8217;ll need to do though: you&#8217;ll need to <strong>submit your sitemap</strong> to search engines. This is easy and it&#8217;s a one-time action.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-how-to-submit-your-sitemap-to-search-engines\">How to Submit Your Sitemap to Search Engines</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To submit your sitemap to Google and Bing you&#8217;ll create a free account with <a href=\"https://search.google.com/search-console/about\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Google Search Console</a> and <a href=\"https://www.bing.com/webmasters/about\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Bing Webmaster Tools</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, follow these instructions.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/submitting-a-sitemap-to-google/\">Submit your sitemap to Google</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/submitting-a-sitemap-to-bing/\">Submit your sitemap to Bing</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-optional-add-an-html-sitemap\">Optional: Add an HTML Sitemap</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Unlike an XML or RSS sitemap, an HTML sitemap is designed for website <em>visitors</em> to read.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition to providing another way users can browse your content, an HTML sitemap can <strong>boost your SEO</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To add an HTML sitemap in All in One SEO, follow these steps.</p>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Open your WordPress editor.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Go to <strong>AIOSEO</strong> <strong>» Sitemaps.</strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Click on HTML Sitemap </strong>then click<strong> Enable Sitemap.</strong></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"536\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-html-sitemap-settings-1024x536.png\" alt=\"aioseo html sitemap feature\" class=\"wp-image-185265\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-html-sitemap-settings-1024x536.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-html-sitemap-settings-300x157.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-html-sitemap-settings-768x402.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-html-sitemap-settings-600x314.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-html-sitemap-settings-115x60.png 115w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-html-sitemap-settings-172x90.png 172w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-html-sitemap-settings.png 1413w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Read more about <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/html-sitemap/\">HTML sitemaps here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-other-sitemaps-available-in-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">Other Sitemaps Available in All in One SEO (AIOSEO)</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Users of the Pro version of AIOSEO have the option to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/how-to-create-a-video-sitemap/\">turn on a <strong>video sitemap</strong></a> or a<a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/how-to-create-a-google-news-sitemap/\"> <strong>Google News sitemap</strong></a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The latter is for <strong>journalism publishers</strong> that want their content to show up in searches in google.com/news.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Publishers need to <a href=\"https://support.google.com/news/publisher-center/answer/9606538\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">apply to Google</a> for approval before their content can be included in Google News.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-project-2-local-seo-for-small-businesses\">Project 2: Local SEO (for Small Businesses)</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you own a small business, then you&#8217;ll want to use the Local SEO feature in All in One SEO (AIOSEO).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the WordPress dashboard, go to <strong>AIOSEO</strong> <strong>» Local SEO.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"454\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-1024x454.jpg\" alt=\"aioseo local seo\" class=\"wp-image-154766\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-1024x454.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-300x133.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-768x340.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-1536x680.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-2048x907.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-600x266.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-135x60.jpg 135w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-203x90.jpg 203w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you&#8217;ll see 3 tabs: <strong>Locations</strong>, <strong>Opening Hours</strong>, and <strong>Maps</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"478\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-1024x478.png\" alt=\"aioseo local seo settings\" class=\"wp-image-154770\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-1024x478.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-300x140.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-768x359.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-600x280.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-128x60.png 128w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-193x90.png 193w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings.png 1353w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Click each tab and scroll down. You&#8217;ll see prompts to fill in information. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you&#8217;re done, click <strong>Save</strong> <strong>Change</strong>s.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For more information see the instructions for:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/local-business-seo-for-a-single-location/\">Single location</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/local-business-seo-for-multiple-locations/\">Multiple locations</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>By activating the Local SEO features and filling out the form, <em>schema markup</em> will be added to your site. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is code that enables Google to better understand your business information. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-theme-notice-box\" role=\"alert\">\n<p>Local businesses can also sign up for a free <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-google-business-profile-to-imrpove-local-seo/\" title=\"\"><strong>Google Business Profile</strong></a>. This is important for boosting your rankings in local search results.</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that we&#8217;ve handled sitemaps and gotten local SEO started, let&#8217;s move on to web page optimizations.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-project-3-optimize-content-for-seo\">Project 3: Optimize Content for SEO</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Optimizing content for SEO <em>begins</em> with choosing a focus keyword that you want the page to rank for. It&#8217;s best to choose the keyword<em> before</em> you create the content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can think of this keyword as the <strong>main topic</strong> of the article.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For this exercise, we&#8217;ll assume you have a web page you want to optimize for a <strong>focus keyword</strong> (also called a focus keyphrase).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once your article is complete, you&#8217;ll want to check AIOSEO&#8217;s recommendations for improvement. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>To see these, in the WordPress dashboard go to<strong> AIOSEO » General.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"424\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-general-settings-1024x424.jpg\" alt=\"aioseo general settings\" class=\"wp-image-185268\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-general-settings-1024x424.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-general-settings-300x124.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-general-settings-768x318.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-general-settings-600x248.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-general-settings-145x60.jpg 145w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-general-settings-217x90.jpg 217w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-general-settings.jpg 1433w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Be sure to click on <strong>Focus Keyphrase</strong> and type your target keyword in.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"532\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-1024x532.jpg\" alt=\"aioseo focus keyphrase\" class=\"wp-image-185270\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-1024x532.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-300x156.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-768x399.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-600x312.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-116x60.jpg 116w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-173x90.jpg 173w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-focus-keyphrase.jpg 1433w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ll get an SEO score out of 100 along with simple suggestions for improvement.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>These recommendations will cover use of your keyword and other basic SEO checks.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For instance, AIOSEO may recommend that you add your keyword to the article description.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Or if your article doesn&#8217;t have any <strong>internal links</strong>, then you&#8217;ll see a suggestion to add one.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/truseo-basic-seo-list-792x1024.png\" alt=\"aioseo basic seo recommendations\" class=\"wp-image-185298\" width=\"396\" height=\"512\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/truseo-basic-seo-list-792x1024.png 792w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/truseo-basic-seo-list-232x300.png 232w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/truseo-basic-seo-list-768x993.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/truseo-basic-seo-list-600x776.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/truseo-basic-seo-list-46x60.png 46w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/truseo-basic-seo-list-70x90.png 70w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/truseo-basic-seo-list.png 947w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 396px) 100vw, 396px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All in One SEO will also do some <strong>readability checks</strong> on your article too. You&#8217;ll get recommendations for readability, such as using shorter paragraphs and sentences.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As you follow the recommendations you&#8217;ll see your score increase. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-about-your-seo-score\">About Your SEO Score</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Please note that the goal isn&#8217;t to get a score of 100. It&#8217;s to see the impact of improvements. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>So consider a score of around 75-80 or above to be good.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As with all digital tools, use your own judgment when deciding whether to accept the recommendations.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A good rule of thumb is to always edit with the reader in mind, rather than for search engines.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-project-4-optimize-titles-and-meta-descriptions\">Project 4: Optimize Titles and Meta Descriptions</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Titles and meta descriptions are important for SEO. A simple principle is to include your target keyword in both.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In a standard search snippet (or search result) a web page looks like this.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"213\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/standard-search-snippet-example-1024x213.png\" alt=\"standard search snippet\" class=\"wp-image-185274\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/standard-search-snippet-example-1024x213.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/standard-search-snippet-example-300x62.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/standard-search-snippet-example-768x159.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/standard-search-snippet-example-600x125.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/standard-search-snippet-example-190x39.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/standard-search-snippet-example-434x90.png 434w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/standard-search-snippet-example.png 1296w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We see a title, link, and description. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Good titles and descriptions are descriptive and precise.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the example above, we learn that Kate Murtaugh Events &amp; Design is located in <strong>New England</strong>, with offices in <strong>Boston</strong> and <strong>Watch Hill,</strong> and they design <strong>luxury weddings </strong>and other <strong>events.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>That&#8217;s an excellent use of the short space available for titles and meta descriptions.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-how-to-use-the-snippet-preview-to-optimize-titles-and-meta-descriptions\">How to Use the Snippet Preview to Optimize Titles and Meta Descriptions</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In AIOSEO there&#8217;s a <strong>Snippet Preview</strong> feature that shows you what your article may look like in Google search results.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To find the Snippet Preview, in your WordPress editor go to <strong>AIOSEO » General. </strong>Then click on <strong>Snippet Preview</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"946\" height=\"415\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-snippet-preview.png\" alt=\"aioseo snippet preview\" class=\"wp-image-185276\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-snippet-preview.png 946w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-snippet-preview-300x132.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-snippet-preview-768x337.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-snippet-preview-600x263.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-snippet-preview-137x60.png 137w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-snippet-preview-205x90.png 205w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Before publishing an article, it&#8217;s good to check this Snippet Preview and use its suggestions to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-serp-snippet-tool/\" title=\"\">optimize your title and meta description</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The recommendations in the Snippet Preview will be related to title and description <em>length</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"aioseo-title-length-considerations\">Title Length Considerations</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Titles tend to get cut off by Google after 60 characters or so. So whatever you want searchers to see should be within the 60-character limit.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"233\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-1024x233.png\" alt=\"search snippet truncated\" class=\"wp-image-177440\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-1024x233.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-300x68.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-768x174.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-600x136.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-190x43.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-396x90.png 396w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated.png 1206w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>When Google cuts a title off, it will places ellipses where the missing words are.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>That said, Google doesn&#8217;t care how long your title is. And it can be helpful to add another keyword or two after the typical cut-off point. This can cause your article to surface in more search queries.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, let&#8217;s say you want to publish an article called:</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">&#8220;<strong>10 Ways to Grow Your YouTube Channel</strong>.&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That&#8217;s only 36 characters. We&#8217;ve got more we can use. So let&#8217;s make our title more specific so readers have a better idea of what the article&#8217;s about.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">&#8220;<strong>10 Ways to Grow Your YouTube Channel <em>to 1k Subscribers</em></strong>&#8220;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We&#8217;re at 54 characters now. We only have 6 characters left. Not much. But let&#8217;s say this article is for beginners. Let&#8217;s go intentionally over the character limit, like this:</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">&#8220;<strong>10 Ways to Grow Your YouTube Channel <em>to 1k Subscribers (Beginner&#8217;s Guide)</em></strong>&#8220;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now we&#8217;re at 72 characters, but the most important part of the title will display in search results and people searching for a beginner&#8217;s article may be likelier to find this one since the word &#8220;beginner&#8217;s&#8221; is included in the title.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Learn more about the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-serp-snippet-tool/\" title=\"\">Snippet Preview features</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"aioseo-meta-description-length-considerations\">Meta Description Length Considerations</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The Snippet Preview will flag any meta description that&#8217;s over <strong>160 characters</strong>. Unlike titles, it&#8217;s best to always keep your meta descriptions <em>within</em> this limit.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"316\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/meta-description-length-1024x316.png\" alt=\"diy seo meta description field\" class=\"wp-image-185279\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/meta-description-length-1024x316.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/meta-description-length-300x93.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/meta-description-length-768x237.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/meta-description-length-600x185.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/meta-description-length-190x60.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/meta-description-length-292x90.png 292w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/meta-description-length.png 1141w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-more-diy-seo-projects\">More DIY SEO Projects</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Congratulations! You&#8217;ve got a sitemap set up and you&#8217;ve learned the basics optimizing pages for SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Where to go from here?</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-learn-how-to-do-keyword-research\">Learn How to Do Keyword Research</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To get traction with SEO, learn how to do keyword research to plan content. Don&#8217;t worry, there&#8217;s an <a href=\"https://www.blogtyrant.com/how-to-easily-find-the-best-keywords/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">easy beginner&#8217;s guide</a> here to follow.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let&#8217;s cover some basics here though.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We mentioned that a focus keyword is similar to a topic. Creating content based on a target keyword is essential for SEO. But here are some important shortcuts to know that will keep you from wasting time.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"aioseo-pick-long-tail-keywords-as-topics-for-new-content\">Pick Long-Tail Keywords as Topics for New Content</h4>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/long-tail-keywords/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">Long-tail keywords</a> are detailed and specific. They typically are not as hard to rank for as broader keywords.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>While they also don&#8217;t get as much traffic as broader keywords, if chosen well, long-tails <em>convert at a higher rate</em>. And in the end, it&#8217;s conversions and sales that matter not the amount of traffic you got that didn&#8217;t convert.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Marketers use SEO tools like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Ahrefs</a> and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Semrush</a> to find out what the average search volume is for a given keyword and how hard it is to rank for it.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Search volume</strong> is the estimated amount of monthly searches for that keyword.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Keyword difficulty</strong> is a numeric score that gives you an idea of how hard it is to rank for a keyword.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"314\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ahrefs-floating-floor-keyword-1024x314.png\" alt=\"ahrefs keyword data example\" class=\"wp-image-185285\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ahrefs-floating-floor-keyword-1024x314.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ahrefs-floating-floor-keyword-300x92.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ahrefs-floating-floor-keyword-768x235.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ahrefs-floating-floor-keyword-1536x471.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ahrefs-floating-floor-keyword-2048x628.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ahrefs-floating-floor-keyword-600x184.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ahrefs-floating-floor-keyword-190x58.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ahrefs-floating-floor-keyword-294x90.png 294w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Above: We used Ahrefs to research the term “<strong>what is a floating floor</strong>.” This term has a Keyword Difficulty score of “Easy” and the Search Volume is 1.2k/month.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>To grow your site, focus on <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/long-tail-keywords/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">long-tail keywords</a> with low difficulty rankings and that are getting a decent amount of traffic.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-link-building-and-metrics\">Link Building and Metrics</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you&#8217;re comfortable with basic SEO and keyword research, consider exploring link building and metrics.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Link-building is a powerful SEO technique. There are 2 types of links involved in link-building:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Internal links</strong> (links within your website)</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Backlinks</strong> (links from other sites to yours).</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are 2 easy ways to get started.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-easily-find-and-fix-orphan-pages-in-wordpress/\">Fix orphan pages</a>. (These are pages with no links from your other web pages. Orphan pages are hard for people and search engines to find.)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Consider providing a guest article to a respected website in return for being able to include a link back to your site.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"583\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-link-assistant-1024x583.png\" alt=\"aioseo link assistant\" class=\"wp-image-166319\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-link-assistant-1024x583.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-link-assistant-300x171.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-link-assistant-768x437.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-link-assistant-600x341.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-link-assistant-105x60.png 105w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-link-assistant-158x90.png 158w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-link-assistant.png 1220w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>All in One SEO&#8217;s Link Assistant makes internal link building easy. (Available in the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"\">Pro version</a>.)</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-metrics-measure-page-speed-and-google-analytics\">Measuring Success</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Lastly, you&#8217;ll want to start measuring your website performance.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All in One SEO (AIOSEO) automatically conducts an <strong>SEO audit</strong> and provides a score for your <em>homepage</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Just like for your individual pages, you&#8217;ll get an to-do list for improving SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This video will walk you through the how-tos. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"How To Perform an SEO Analysis On Your WordPress Website\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/KZKPaFlotDo?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-set-up-google-analytics-on-a-wordpress-site/\">Google Analytics</a> is the go-to tool for measuring traffic and SEO results. It&#8217;s a free tool and Google also offers excellent training for beginners to get you up to speed.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That said, Google is so generous with the amount of free data it gives you, that some may find it overwhelming.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Try the interface out. If you feel it seems complicated, consider using the <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">MonsterInsights</a> WordPress plugin. It presents the most important numbers right in your WordPress dashboard.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"636\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/monsterinsights-dashboard-1024x636.webp\" alt=\"monsterinsights dashboard\" class=\"wp-image-144240\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/monsterinsights-dashboard-1024x636.webp 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/monsterinsights-dashboard-300x186.webp 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/monsterinsights-dashboard-768x477.webp 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/monsterinsights-dashboard-1536x954.webp 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/monsterinsights-dashboard-2048x1272.webp 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/monsterinsights-dashboard-600x373.webp 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/monsterinsights-dashboard-97x60.webp 97w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/monsterinsights-dashboard-145x90.webp 145w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>MonsterInsights&#8217; dashboard</em>.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-more-seo-tips\">More DIY SEO tips</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As you read more about creating SEO-optimized content, keep these tips in mind.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Google rewards <strong>quality content</strong>. So don&#8217;t get tied in knots about following a bunch of rules. Keep quality as your #1 principle.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Decide who your <strong>target audience</strong> is before writing.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Avoid <strong>keyword stuffing</strong>: this is an old practice of adding a target keyword to a page numerous times in hopes of boosting its ranking.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Learn how to <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/image-alt-text-vs-image-title-in-wordpress-whats-the-difference/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">add <strong>alt tags</strong></a> to images in this article.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-summing-it-up\">Summing it Up</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Congratulations! You&#8217;ve built the foundation for your SEO strategy, by setting up your sitemaps, learning about on-page optimizations, and learning how to use a WordPress SEO plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You also got an introduction to some more advanced concepts like link building and metrics.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With SEO experts charging high fees, taking a do-it-yourself approach can save you a lot of money.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-whats-next\">What&#8217;s Next?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you get started with some enjoyable DIY SEO projects.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, explore <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/link-building-guide/\" title=\"\">link building</a> and check out our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-tutorial/\" title=\"\">SEO tutorial for beginners</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more step-by-step tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/diy-seo-projects-for-beginners/\">DIY SEO: 4 Easy Projects to Get Started</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://aioseo.com/diy-seo-projects-for-beginners/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"Announcing Content Rankings: SEO Performance Tracking Made Easy\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:188:\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-content-rankings-seo-performance-tracking-made-easy/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=announcing-content-rankings-seo-performance-tracking-made-easy\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:91:\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-content-rankings-seo-performance-tracking-made-easy/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 02 May 2023 14:07:52 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"Content Rankings\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"Google Search Console integration\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"SEO perfomance monitoring\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=183508\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:520:\"<p>We’ve just rolled out AIOSEO 4.3.6 and have some exciting news! We&#8217;re thrilled to announce the addition of the Content Rankings report to our powerful Search Statistics module. The Content Rankings report makes tracking your content&#8217;s performance on search engine&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-content-rankings-seo-performance-tracking-made-easy/\">Announcing Content Rankings: SEO Performance Tracking Made Easy</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Benjamin Rojas\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11099:\"<p>We’ve just rolled out AIOSEO 4.3.6 and have some exciting news!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We&#8217;re thrilled to announce the addition of the Content Rankings report to our powerful Search Statistics module. The Content Rankings report makes tracking your content&#8217;s performance on search engine results pages (SERPs) easy. You can easily spot content decay and identify significant trends.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let’s quickly take a deep dive into the Content Rankings report and why it’s helpful to your SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-gray-light-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-keep-tabs-on-content-performance-directly-in-wordpress\">Keep Tabs on Content Performance Directly in WordPress</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-identify-content-trends-to-boost-your-search-rankings\">Identify Content Trends to Boost Your Search Rankings</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-monitor-for-content-decay\">Monitor for Content Decay</a></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Announcing Content Rankings: SEO Performance Tracking Made Easy\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dnzFdU0wvBg?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-keep-tabs-on-content-performance-directly-in-wordpress\">Keep Tabs on Content Performance Directly in WordPress&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We added the Content Rankings report to help you understand how your content performs on SERPs. This powerful report gives insights into your content’s performance on search engine results pages (SERPs) over the past 12 months.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"370\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-report-1.png\" alt=\"The Content Rankings report gives insights into your content’s performance on search engine results pages (SERPs).\" class=\"wp-image-183514\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-report-1.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-report-1-300x159.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-report-1-600x317.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-report-1-114x60.png 114w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-report-1-170x90.png 170w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Content Rankings report highlights many essential SEO and content marketing metrics, such as:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Last Updated On</strong>: Shows the date a URL was last updated. This helps you easily track the impact of any change you make on a particular page or post.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Loss</strong>: This shows the rate at which your content is decaying. This is based on our proprietary content decay algorithm, which considers an article’s impressions and clickthrough rates (CTR), among other factors.&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Drop (%)</strong>: The percentage drop/gain in content decay points.&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Performance Score</strong>: This is a visual overview of your content&#8217;s performance over the past 12 months.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>But that’s not all!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>When you click on a page or post on the report, you get detailed SEO data about the URL. You can view the Headline Score, TrueSEO score, page load speed, and a links report from Link Assistant.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"455\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-report-data-1.png\" alt=\"Content Rankings also shows SEO data like the Headline Score, TrueSEO score, page load speed, and more.\" class=\"wp-image-183516\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-report-data-1.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-report-data-1-300x195.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-report-data-1-600x390.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-report-data-1-92x60.png 92w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-report-data-1-138x90.png 138w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides this data, you also get an overview of the page’s SEO metadata, redirects, and SEO performance.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"374\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-report-data-2.png\" alt=\"Content Rankings also gives you an overview of the page’s metadata, redirects, and SEO performance.\" class=\"wp-image-183517\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-report-data-2.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-report-data-2-300x160.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-report-data-2-600x321.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-report-data-2-112x60.png 112w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-report-data-2-168x90.png 168w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, the Content Rankings report has a Keyword Performance section. This shows you all the keywords your page ranks for, including those performing well and those dropping in rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"401\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/how-to-track-seo-keyword-rankings-top-losing.png\" alt=\"You also get a report that shows your keyword performance.\" class=\"wp-image-177220\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/how-to-track-seo-keyword-rankings-top-losing.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/how-to-track-seo-keyword-rankings-top-losing-300x171.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/how-to-track-seo-keyword-rankings-top-losing-600x343.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/how-to-track-seo-keyword-rankings-top-losing-105x60.png 105w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/how-to-track-seo-keyword-rankings-top-losing-158x90.png 158w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All this data makes the Content Ranking report a powerful tool that gives you the insights to optimize your content and drive more traffic to your site.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-identify-content-trends-to-boost-your-search-rankings\">Identify Content Trends to Boost Your Search Rankings</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You can use the Performance Score column in the Content Rankings report to quickly see how your content performs in search results over time.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"332\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-performance-score.png\" alt=\"The Performance Score column shows your content\'s performs in search results over the past 12 months.\" class=\"wp-image-183518\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-performance-score.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-performance-score-300x142.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-performance-score-600x284.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-performance-score-127x60.png 127w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/content-rankings-performance-score-190x90.png 190w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can identify trends in your search rankings and the content declining in performance. Content can decline in performance because it needs to be optimized for search engines, or probably it’s not matching the search intent.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>By identifying these trends, you can adjust and fine-tune your content strategy to focus on topics more likely to rank in search results.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-monitor-for-content-decay\">Monitor for Content Decay</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Content decay is when content starts losing rankings on SERPs. It could be because the content is outdated, irrelevant, or outperformed by newer and better content. It’s a common problem for all websites that results in a traffic and revenue decline. However, you can reduce the impact of content decay by quickly spotting it and updating your content.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And this is precisely what the Content Rankings report can help you do.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can use it to monitor your posts for signs of decay, as you can easily see which posts are declining in search rankings. As a result, you can quickly update or improve them before it&#8217;s too late.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Overall, the Content Rankings Report is a powerful new feature that can help you take your SEO to the next level. By providing insights into your content’s rankings, you can make informed decisions to improve your content&#8217;s visibility, increase rankings in search results, and combat content decay. It&#8217;s a must-have tool for anyone serious about driving traffic to their content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides this significant update, we’ve made several notable improvements to many features you love. For example, we’ve refreshed our user interface, making it sleeker and more fluid. You can see all our changes in our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/changelog/\" title=\"AIOSEO Changelog\">full product changelog</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What are you waiting for?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Update your site to AIOSEO 4.3.6 to unlock these powerful new features and rank your content higher on SERPs.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And if you’re not yet using AIOSEO, make sure to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">install and activate the plugin today</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have questions about these features, please comment below or <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/contact/\" title=\"Contact Us\">contact our customer support team</a>. We’re always ready to help. Our commitment to making AIOSEO the easiest and best WordPress SEO plugin is only getting stronger as we continue to win together with our customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We’re so grateful for your continued support, feedback, and suggestions. Please keep those suggestions and feature requests coming!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope you enjoy using these new SEO features as much as we enjoyed creating them.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>-Benjamin Rojas (President of AIOSEO).</em></p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-content-rankings-seo-performance-tracking-made-easy/\">Announcing Content Rankings: SEO Performance Tracking Made Easy</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:87:\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-content-rankings-seo-performance-tracking-made-easy/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"Referring Domains vs Backlinks: What’s the Difference (Plus: SEO Impact)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:132:\"https://aioseo.com/referring-domains-vs-backlinks-seo/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=referring-domains-vs-backlinks-seo\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://aioseo.com/referring-domains-vs-backlinks-seo/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 27 Apr 2023 15:30:00 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"SEO Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"backlinks\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"link building\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Referring domains\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Referring domains vs. backlinks\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=182232\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:501:\"<p>Wondering what the difference is between referring domains vs backlinks? If you&#8217;re working on website SEO, you’ve probably seen these terms. And you may know that backlinks are a significant ranking factor. In this article, we&#8217;ll explain the differences between&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/referring-domains-vs-backlinks-seo/\">Referring Domains vs Backlinks: What’s the Difference (Plus: SEO Impact)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Sherrie Gossett\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31524:\"<p>Wondering what the difference is between referring domains vs backlinks?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re working on website SEO, you’ve probably seen these terms. And you may know that backlinks are a significant ranking factor.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll explain the differences between referring domains vs backlinks. And we’ll explain how they impact SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-are-backlinks\">What Are Backlinks?</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-referring-domains-vs-backlinks\">Referring Domains vs Backlinks</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-role-of-backlinks-in-link-building\">Backlinks in Link Building</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-impact-on-seo\">Impact on SEO</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-backlinks-and-big-money\">Backlinks and Big Money</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-start-building-a-backlink-profile\">Start Building a Backlink Profile</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-summing-it-up\">Referring Domains vs Backlinks: Summary</a><ul></ul></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-what-are-backlinks\">What Are Backlinks?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Backlinks are hyperlinks from other websites to yours. In everyday conversation, people may use the term &#8220;link&#8221; instead.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, if we linked to your website from this article page, you could say:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>I got a backlink from aioseo.com, or,</li>\n\n\n\n<li>I got a link from aioseo.com.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Backlinks are a prominent topic in SEO because they&#8217;re a ranking factor.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you obtain a significant number of links from <em>trusted</em> websites, it can increase your sales and revenue.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-backlink-quality-matters-for-rankings\">Backlink Quality Matters for Rankings</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>But quality is key.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Backlinks from low-quality sites can hurt your rankings.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Backlinks from respected websites can boost your rankings.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>So, what&#8217;s considered a low-quality backlink?</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Links from spurious sites like financial scam sites, sites selling illegal drugs, or sites involved in link schemes.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Backlinks from odd websites, like those with almost no content or gibberish content.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>And what&#8217;s considered a high-quality link?</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Links from trusted institutions like government, universities, medical centers, industry and business associations, or mainstream media.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Links from established businesses and subject matter experts.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-how-do-i-find-out-what-backlinks-my-site-has\">How Do I Find Out What Backlinks My Site Has?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To find out what backlinks your website has, create a free account with <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Ahrefs</a> and log in.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>At the top left, enter your domain’s URL.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"116\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-url-field-1-1024x116.png\" alt=\"ahrefs url field\" class=\"wp-image-182476\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-url-field-1-1024x116.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-url-field-1-300x34.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-url-field-1-768x87.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-url-field-1-1536x174.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-url-field-1-2048x232.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-url-field-1-600x68.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-url-field-1-190x22.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-url-field-1-750x85.png 750w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, you&#8217;ll see a dashboard with top indicators including your total number of backlinks.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Click on <strong>Backlinks</strong> to view each individual backlink your site has.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"344\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-dashboard-copy-1024x344.png\" alt=\"ahrefs backlinks analysis\" class=\"wp-image-182478\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-dashboard-copy-1024x344.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-dashboard-copy-300x101.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-dashboard-copy-768x258.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-dashboard-copy-1536x515.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-dashboard-copy-2048x687.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-dashboard-copy-600x201.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-dashboard-copy-179x60.png 179w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-dashboard-copy-268x90.png 268w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, what&#8217;s the difference between backlinks and <em>referring domains</em>?</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-referring-domains-vs-backlinks\">Referring Domains vs Backlinks</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A <strong>referring domain</strong> is a website that has linked to your site; the <strong>backlink</strong> is the URL of the specific page that has linked to you.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, if we link to WPForms.com from this page:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>The <strong>referring domain</strong> would be <strong>aioseo.com</strong>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>The <strong>backlink</strong> would be this page URL: aioseo.com/referring-domains-vs-backlinks-seo</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>In our example in the previous section, we saw that AIOSEO.com has:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>478k backlinks.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking at that same Ahrefs dashboard, we can that AIOSEO.com has:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>7.35k referring domains.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"356\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-referring-domains-1024x356.png\" alt=\"ahrefs referring domains\" class=\"wp-image-182480\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-referring-domains-1024x356.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-referring-domains-300x104.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-referring-domains-768x267.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-referring-domains-1536x534.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-referring-domains-2048x713.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-referring-domains-600x209.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-referring-domains-172x60.png 172w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-referring-domains-259x90.png 259w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Notice that AIOSEO&#8217;s number of referring domains is less than the number of backlinks. This is common. It means that some websites link multiple times to the same website.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-domain-authority-and-domain-ratings\">Domain Authority and Domain Ratings</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before we look at Ahrefs Referring Domains report, take another look at the dashboard.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ll see there&#8217;s a “DR” score, out of 100. DR stands for &#8220;<strong>Domain Rating</strong>.&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"393\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-domain-rating-score-1024x393.png\" alt=\"ahrefs domain rating score\" class=\"wp-image-182482\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-domain-rating-score-1024x393.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-domain-rating-score-300x115.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-domain-rating-score-768x294.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-domain-rating-score-1536x589.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-domain-rating-score-600x230.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-domain-rating-score-157x60.png 157w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-domain-rating-score-235x90.png 235w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-domain-rating-score.png 1920w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This is a proprietary score, measured on a logarithmic scale, that serves as a useful proxy for the quality of a website (domain).</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Semrush</a>, software similar to Ahrefs, provides a similar score called &#8220;Authority Score.&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"546\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/semrush-domain-authority-score-2-1024x546.png\" alt=\"semrush authority score\" class=\"wp-image-182694\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/semrush-domain-authority-score-2-1024x546.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/semrush-domain-authority-score-2-300x160.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/semrush-domain-authority-score-2-768x410.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/semrush-domain-authority-score-2-1536x819.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/semrush-domain-authority-score-2-600x320.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/semrush-domain-authority-score-2-113x60.png 113w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/semrush-domain-authority-score-2-169x90.png 169w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/semrush-domain-authority-score-2.png 2044w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Semrush and Ahrefs measure their domain scores differently. For instance, this website, wpbeginner.com, scores a 90 in <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Ahrefs</a>. </em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The score is intended to help marketing professionals identify high-quality websites. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Domain scores are useful when assessing the quality of a site&#8217;s backlink profile and identifying sites to target in campaigns.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But these scores aren&#8217;t perfect. For example, it&#8217;s possible for domains with a high score to expire, and be purchased by people who then use them for <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/search/docs/essentials/spam-policies#link-spam\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">link schemes</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-theme-notice-box\" role=\"alert\">\n<p>Google&#8217;s algorithms don&#8217;t use domain authority scores.</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-referring-domains-report\">Referring Domains Report</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Now let&#8217;s look at Ahrefs&#8217; <strong>Referring Domains Report </strong>which you can access by clicking on that referring domains number.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ll see a complete list of all domains that have linked to yours. And this sortable list, by default, ranks these domains <em>according to their Domain Rating score</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So at the top of our list of referring domains we see sites with Domain Rating (DR) scores of 90+, including WordPress.org and Github.com.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"629\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-referring-domains-vs-backlinks-1-1024x629.png\" alt=\"ahrefs referring domains report\" class=\"wp-image-183097\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-referring-domains-vs-backlinks-1-1024x629.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-referring-domains-vs-backlinks-1-300x184.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-referring-domains-vs-backlinks-1-768x471.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-referring-domains-vs-backlinks-1-1536x943.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-referring-domains-vs-backlinks-1-600x368.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-referring-domains-vs-backlinks-1-98x60.png 98w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-referring-domains-vs-backlinks-1-147x90.png 147w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-referring-domains-vs-backlinks-1.png 1691w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-role-of-backlinks-in-link-building\">Role of Backlinks in Link Building</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Because quality backlinks can mean more traffic and revenue, many businesses hire marketers to run link building campaigns.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A link building campaign is simply any activity designed to increase backlinks to a website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>These campaigns can range from writing guest articles for industry websites all the way up to complex processes involving multiple software platforms and proprietary methods.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Regardless of the link building strategy involved, marketers prize backlinks from high-quality sites.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But why do these links impact SEO?</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-impact-on-seo\">Impact on SEO</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Google views backlinks from trusted sites as a vote of confidence in your site. It&#8217;s like an endorsement.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As more sites give yours that confidence vote, your site&#8217;s pages will likely start to rank higher in search results. Benefits include increases in:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Referral traffic (traffic coming from the linking sites)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Organic traffic (from elevated search rankings)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Conversions and revenue.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, a website with a strong backlink profile can command top dollar in the resale marketplace.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-backlinks-and-big-money\">Backlinks and Big Money</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A strong backlink profile is one factor that attracts corporate buyers or angel investors to personal websites.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Classic car buff Randy Nonnenberg turned his BringATrailer.com blog into a $1 billion marketplace. Notice the strong backlink numbers.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"585\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/bring-a-trailer-1024x585.png\" alt=\"bringatrailer backlinks\" class=\"wp-image-182488\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/bring-a-trailer-1024x585.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/bring-a-trailer-300x171.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/bring-a-trailer-768x439.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/bring-a-trailer-1536x878.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/bring-a-trailer-2048x1171.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/bring-a-trailer-600x343.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/bring-a-trailer-105x60.png 105w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/bring-a-trailer-157x90.png 157w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Hearst Autos acquired BringATrailer in June 2020, at the height of the pandemic. At the time, the site had a strong backlink profile.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Since the acquisition, the site has <em>quintupled</em> its referring domains number, an indication that the new owners are prioritizing link building.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"392\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/bringatrailer-referring-domains-1024x392.png\" alt=\"bringatrailer referring domains growth\" class=\"wp-image-182490\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/bringatrailer-referring-domains-1024x392.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/bringatrailer-referring-domains-300x115.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/bringatrailer-referring-domains-768x294.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/bringatrailer-referring-domains-1536x588.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/bringatrailer-referring-domains-2048x784.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/bringatrailer-referring-domains-600x230.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/bringatrailer-referring-domains-157x60.png 157w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/bringatrailer-referring-domains-235x90.png 235w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Ahrefs chart of BringATrailer.com’s referring domains growth from 2014 on.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This hockey stick pattern showing little growth followed by a dramatic spike in referring domains to a site, isn’t uncommon.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The CleverGirlFinance.com blog only had 165 referring domains in 2018, and now they’re at 7.54k with 211k backlinks and a total monthly traffic value of <strong>$203k</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"198\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-clevergirlfinance-backlinks-1-1024x198.png\" alt=\"clevergirlfinance referring domains vs. backlinks\" class=\"wp-image-183109\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-clevergirlfinance-backlinks-1-1024x198.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-clevergirlfinance-backlinks-1-300x58.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-clevergirlfinance-backlinks-1-768x148.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-clevergirlfinance-backlinks-1-1536x297.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-clevergirlfinance-backlinks-1-2048x396.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-clevergirlfinance-backlinks-1-600x116.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-clevergirlfinance-backlinks-1-190x37.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/ahrefs-clevergirlfinance-backlinks-1-465x90.png 465w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>What’s<strong> traffic value</strong>? This metric means that the site owner would have to spend $203k/month in <em>search advertising</em> to get the same amount (and quality) of traffic she’s getting for free from <em>search engines</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is the power of SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"973\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/clever-girl-finance-referring-domains2-973x1024.png\" alt=\"clevergirlfinance referring domains growth\" class=\"wp-image-182493\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/clever-girl-finance-referring-domains2-973x1024.png 973w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/clever-girl-finance-referring-domains2-285x300.png 285w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/clever-girl-finance-referring-domains2-768x808.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/clever-girl-finance-referring-domains2-1460x1536.png 1460w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/clever-girl-finance-referring-domains2-1946x2048.png 1946w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/clever-girl-finance-referring-domains2-600x631.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/clever-girl-finance-referring-domains2-57x60.png 57w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/clever-girl-finance-referring-domains2-86x90.png 86w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>The</em> <em>Ahrefs dashboard shows exponential growth in referring domains for CleverGirlFinance.com. Angel investor Jonathan Cornelissen has </em><a href=\"https://medium.com/@jonathan_cornelissen/why-i-invested-in-clever-girl-finance-610ce14d1f\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\"><em>invested</em></a><em> in the site.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The moral of the story?</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Everyone starts small.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>It takes consistent discipline to grow.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Persistence matters.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-to-start-building-a-backlink-profile\">How to Start Building a Backlink Profile</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s difficult to get backlinks from government or university websites. Some of these sites have policies against linking to commercial enterprises.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Start by getting backlinks from trusted sites you have some relevance to.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Consider these options:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Small local news sites</strong>: Write an OpEd for a local news site in return for a link to your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Industry associations: </strong>Whether these are local, regional, or national, consider a membership if you’ll get a link in return. Or offer to write a guest post in return for a backlink.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Chambers of commerce: </strong>These typically offer you a link in an online members&#8217; directory. There will be a few hundred dollars or so to join. As you network with the chamber members, consider requesting backlinks as people voice support for your business.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Community programs</strong> <strong>and causes</strong>: If you support local events or causes, request a backlink in return for your sponsorship.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Guest blogging</strong>: Offer to write a few guest posts for related blogs or industry news sites.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>High-quality content</strong>: Start by creating 1-3 high-quality articles for your site. This will attract links.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-what-to-avoid\">What to Avoid</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Skip the infographics</strong>: Interest in infographics has died down. Plus, they aren&#8217;t easy to navigate on mobile phones.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Don&#8217;t guest post for irrelevant sites</strong>: If you sell cowboy hats, don&#8217;t guest post for a site selling ballet shoes.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Nofollow links:</strong> Learn the difference between <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/wordpress-table-of-contents-seo/#aioseo-nofollow-vs-dofollow-links-whats-the-difference\">nofollow and dofollow links</a>. Nofollow links signal to search engines that the linking site <em>does not endorse</em> your site. So while you&#8217;ll get referral <em>traffic</em> from the links, you won’t get any SEO value.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-theres-more-to-seo-strategy-than-just-backlinks\">There’s More to SEO Strategy than Just Backlinks</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To make the most of SEO impact from backlinks be sure to adopt a sound SEO strategy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is where a plugin like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">All in One SEO (AIOSEO)</a> comes in. Created for WordPress users, it makes technical tasks as easy as clicking some buttons and filling out some form fields.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"485\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png\" alt=\"aioseo homepage\" class=\"wp-image-140989\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-300x142.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-768x364.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-600x284.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-127x60.png 127w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-190x90.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage.png 1260w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All in One SEO (AIOSEO) is an established plugin with over 3 million users. And it has thousands of 5-star reviews on WordPress.org.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">download the plugin here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-on-page-seo\">On-Page SEO</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>All in One SEO (AIOSEO) analyzes your content for you. For each web page, it provides a beginner-friendly <strong>checklist</strong> for you to take action on.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Optimizing your content for SEO is a key part of attracting backlinks: as your content rises in search engine rankings, more people will discover it and link to it.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"916\" height=\"568\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-focus-keyword.png\" alt=\"aioseo focus keyword use\" class=\"wp-image-183113\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-focus-keyword.png 916w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-focus-keyword-300x186.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-focus-keyword-768x476.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-focus-keyword-600x372.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-focus-keyword-97x60.png 97w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-focus-keyword-145x90.png 145w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>An example of one of All in One SEO’s on-page recommendations.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This plugin also provides a click-button way to add schema markup to your web pages. This is code that makes your page eligible to be displayed as a rich snippet in search results.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can think of <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-rich-snippets-to-wordpress/\" title=\"\">rich snippets</a> as super-deluxe search engine displays. Here’s an example.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"564\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-1024x564.jpg\" alt=\"rich snippet example\" class=\"wp-image-183115\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-1024x564.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-300x165.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-768x423.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-1536x846.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-2048x1127.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-600x330.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-109x60.jpg 109w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-163x90.jpg 163w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>It’s not surprising that <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-product-rich-snippets-in-wordpress/\" title=\"\">rich snippets</a> lead to higher click-through rates (CTRs). (Source: Milestone Research </em><a href=\"https://blog.milestoneinternet.com/seo/seo-click-curves-get-58-clicks-per-100/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\"><em>study</em></a><em>)</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-internal-links\">Internal Links</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Internal links play a role in SEO too.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO’s <strong>Link Assistant</strong> (available with the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"\">Pro version</a>) makes adding internal links fast and simple.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Link Assistant will tell you <em>which</em> pages need links.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>It will provide an easy way to add links, without opening the pages.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pro tips</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Make sure you have plenty of internal links pointing to your most important pages.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>And deal with <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-easily-find-and-fix-orphan-pages-in-wordpress/\">orphan</a> pages by adding at least one internal link.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"587\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-link-assistant-dashboard-1-1024x587.png\" alt=\"aioseo link assistant dashboard\" class=\"wp-image-142484\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-link-assistant-dashboard-1-1024x587.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-link-assistant-dashboard-1-300x172.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-link-assistant-dashboard-1-768x440.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-link-assistant-dashboard-1-600x344.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-link-assistant-dashboard-1-105x60.png 105w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-link-assistant-dashboard-1-157x90.png 157w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-link-assistant-dashboard-1.png 1247w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Inside Link Assistant, click on “Orphaned Posts” to find a list of web pages that need internal links.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-do-social-media-backlinks-count-for-seo\">Do Social Media Backlinks Count for SEO?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>No, social media backlinks do not contribute to SEO. This is because these links are &#8220;nofollow&#8221; links. Nofollow links contain code that tells search engines &#8220;We don&#8217;t endorse the site we&#8217;re linking to.&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Social media links, like all inbound links, may provide <em>referral</em> traffic, but they won’t impact search engine rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-bonus-tips\">Bonus Tips</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Use a free tool like Google Analytics to track website metrics. And consider simplifying things by using <a href=\"https://www.exactmetrics.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">ExactMetrics</a> or <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">MonsterInsights</a>. These WordPress plugins pull data from Google Analytics and display just what you need to know.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Bookmark this blog for more search engine optimization and digital marketing tips.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-summing-it-up\">Referring Domains vs Backlinks: Summary</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Both referring domains and backlinks play a role in website rankings, and link building can boost your organic search traffic (i.e., traffic from search engines).</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Focus on getting <em>high-quality</em> backlinks more than on the total number of links.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-whats-next\">What’s Next?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you understand the difference between referring domains vs backlinks and how both can make an impact on your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, explore this <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/link-building-guide/\" title=\"\">guide to link building</a> and this explainer on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/nofollow-vs-dofollow-links/\" title=\"\">nofollow vs dofollow links</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/referring-domains-vs-backlinks-seo/\">Referring Domains vs Backlinks: What’s the Difference (Plus: SEO Impact)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"https://aioseo.com/referring-domains-vs-backlinks-seo/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"9 Best SEO Keyword Analysis Tools You Need to Know in 2023\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:124:\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-keyword-analysis-tool/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=best-seo-keyword-analysis-tool\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://aioseo.co